      "span_text": "Compositional skew was estimated using the following formulas: GC skew = (G − C)/(G + C) and AT skew = (A − T)/(A + T), where C, G, A, and T are the frequencies of the four bases at the third codon position of the eight fourfold degenerate codon families [CITATION_1] ."
